{"type":"message","id":"c75255fc","parentId":"2745f0f5","timestamp":"2026-04-16T06:25:05.531Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，大哥。新文档已创建成功，但旧文档无法直接删除。\n\n**当前状态：**\n- **新文档**：`RAG 系统开发项目进度报告（v2）`，链接：https://feishu.cn/docx/O7eBdIJSdo8LQlxIEaVcAaa3n2f\n- **旧文档**：`RAG 系统开发项目进度报告`，链接：https://feishu.cn/docx/ZOg3dhgGFouPgFxKn5FcOZRknnb（无法删除）\n\n**下一步：**\n我将立即将**新文档链接**同步给小策和小栈，请他们使用新文档更新进度。旧文档无法删除，但新文档已创建，不影响使用。\n\n**立即执行：**\n通过 `sessions_send` 将新文档链接发送给小策和小栈。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6aa349881462496eab594142","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:project_manager:feishu:project_manager:direct:ou_86e05fde861d65cbcc06f6e732d0b11d","message":"【项目进度报告已更新】\n\n大哥已新建云文档：**RAG 系统开发项目进度报告（v2）**\n\n🔗 文档链接：https://feishu.cn/docx/O7eBdIJSdo8LQlxIEaVcAaa3n2f\n\n**当前进度摘要：**\n- 技术选型：LlamaIndex（推荐）\n- 下一步：小范围跑通流程（1-2 小时），输出配置模板和示例代码\n- 行动：小策和小栈同步开始执行，请定期更新此文档。\n\n请同步更新进度，谢谢！"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"vllm","model":"qwen3.5-9b","usage":{"input":38959,"output":404,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39363,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776320700511,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a30486d529e18525"}}
