{"type":"message","id":"e7fa710f","parentId":"6d5aec3d","timestamp":"2026-04-16T06:52:43.843Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_35152262934a496399702571","toolName":"sessions_history","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:subagent:9281cd23-d4c3-4541-94b6-2a0d033fa3f1\",\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"[Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\\n\\n[Subagent Task]: 【任务背景】\\n大哥指派：在 /home/zigaa/.openclaw/workspace/workspace-develop 目录下，开发一个简单的 RAG（检索增强生成）系统。\\n\\n【技术选型结论】\\n- **推荐技术栈**：LlamaIndex（项目经理小策已确认）\\n- **理由**：专注 RAG 场景，轻量快速，适合 MVP。\\n\\n【核心开发步骤】\\n1. **环境搭建**：创建虚拟环境，安装 llama-index 核心包 + 所需组件\\n2. **数据准备与清洗**：收集原始文档，编写数据清洗脚本，分割为 chunk\\n3. **索引构建**：选择向量数据库（Chroma/FAISS/Milvus），配置嵌入模型，构建索引\\n4. **查询处理**：实现查询理解与重排序，配置检索策略，设计 prompt 模板\\n5. **模型选择**：嵌入模型、LLM、重排序模型\\n6. **部署与测试**：封装为 API 服务，编写测试用例，监控日志与性能指标\\n\\n【当前阶段】\\n- 先在小范围数据上跑通完整流程（1-2 小时）\\n- 输出可复用的配置模板和示例代码\\n\\n【行动要求】\\n1. 立即开始**环境搭建**和**数据清洗脚本**的开发。\\n2. 定期更新项目进度报告（云文档链接：https://feishu.cn/docx/O7eBdIJSdo8LQlxIEaVcAaa3n2f）。\\n3. 如有问题，及时与小策或大哥沟通。\\n\\n**需要立即开始执行吗？**\\n\\n[Bootstrap truncation warning]\\nSome workspace bootstrap files were truncated before injection.\\nTreat Project Context as partial and read the relevant files directly if details seem missing.\\n- AGENTS.md: 7727 raw -> 4608 injected (~40% removed; max/file).\\n- If unintentional, raise agents.defaults.bootstrapMaxChars and/or agents.defaults.bootstrapTotalMaxChars.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1776321469827,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"8d67f3d7\",\n        \"seq\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"好的，大哥。我理解任务：在 `workspace-develop` 目录下使用 LlamaIndex 快速搭建一个 RA