{"type":"message","id":"2891c84d","parentId":"2172f396","timestamp":"2026-04-16T06:56:07.669Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，大哥。llama-index 核心包已成功安装！\n\n**下一步行动：**\n1.  **编写数据清洗脚本**：将文档分割为 chunk。\n2.  **同步进度**：将执行进度同步给小策和大哥。\n\n**立即执行：编写数据清洗脚本。**\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f5f0c99ffbb748f981c5488d","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/zigaa/.openclaw/workspace/workspace-develop/data_cleaner.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"vllm","model":"qwen3.5-9b","usage":{"input":59540,"output":8192,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67732,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776322468590,"responseId":"chatcmpl-bd1e6983aa38c27d"}}
