{"type":"message","id":"654c1377","parentId":"73195eea","timestamp":"2026-04-16T07:47:34.326Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，大哥。FAISS 保存失败（目录已存在）。我将修复保存逻辑。\n\n**立即执行：修复 FAISS 保存（删除旧文件或保存到子目录）。**\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dbac1595d73142f28b5f2cf2","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/zigaa/.openclaw/workspace/workspace-develop/rag_service_custom.py","edits":"[{\"oldText\": \"# 添加索引\\nprint(\\\"\\\\n添加索引...\\\")\\nfaiss_index.add(embeddings)\\nfaiss.write_index(faiss_index, faiss_dir)\\nprint(f\\\"  索引保存成功：{faiss_dir}\\\")\", \"newText\": \"# 添加索引\\nprint(\\\"\\\\n添加索引...\\\")\\nfaiss_index.add(embeddings)\\n# 保存到子目录（避免覆盖目录）\\nfaiss_dir_file = faiss_dir + \\\"/index.faiss\\\"\\nos.makedirs(os.path.dirname(faiss_dir_file), exist_ok=True)\\nfaiss.write_index(faiss_index, faiss_dir_file)\\nprint(f\\\"  索引保存成功：{faiss_dir_file}\\\")\"}]}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"vllm","model":"qwen3.5-9b","usage":{"input":78067,"output":249,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78316,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776325650727,"responseId":"chatcmpl-87c7fde1963d27f8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2ef7296d","parentId":"654c1377","timestamp":"2026-04-16T07:47:34.355Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_dbac1595d73142f28b5f2cf2","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Validation failed for tool \"edit\":\n  - edits: must be array\n\nReceived arguments:\n{\n  \"path\": \"/home/zigaa/.openclaw/workspace/workspace-develop/rag_service_custom.py\",\n  \"edits\": \"[{\\\"oldText\\\": \\\"# 添加索引\\\\nprint(\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\n添加索引...\\\\\\\")\\\\nfaiss_index.add(embeddings)\\\\nfaiss.write_index(faiss_index, faiss_dir)\\\\nprint(f\\\\\\\"  索引保存成功：{faiss_dir}\\\\\\\")\\\", \\\"newText\\\": \\\"# 添加索引\\\\nprint(\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\n添加索引...\\\\\\\")\\\\nfaiss_index.add(embeddings)\\\\n# 保存到子目录（避免覆盖目录）\\\\nfaiss_dir_file = faiss_dir + \\\\\\\"/index.faiss\\\\\\\"\\\\nos.makedirs(os.path.dirname(faiss_dir_file), exist_ok=True)\\\\nfaiss.write_index(faiss_index, faiss_dir_file)\\\\nprint(f\\\\\\\"  索引保存成功：{faiss_dir_file}\\\\\\\")\\\"}]}\"\n}"}],"details":{},"isError":true,"timestamp":1776325654352}}
{"type":"message","id":"cd56ea92","parentId":"2ef7296d","timestamp":"2026-04-16T07:47:51.452Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，大哥。编辑失败，我将直接重写服务脚本，修复 FAISS 保存逻辑。\n\n**立即执行：重写服务脚本（修复 FAISS 保存）。**\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_66cce140bedb4508998e0660","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/zigaa/.openclaw/workspace/workspace-develop/rag_service_custom.py","content":"\"\"\"\nRAG 系统服务 - 自定义 FAISS 版（仅 vLLM + 简化嵌入）\n\n环境：Python 3.12 + uv venv\n技术栈：LlamaIndex + 自定义 FAISS + vLLM（简化嵌入）\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom llama_index.core import VectorStoreIndex, StorageContext, SimpleDirectoryReader\nfrom llama_index.core import ServiceContext, Document\nfrom llama_index.core.node_parser import SentenceSplitter\nfrom llama_index.llms.vllm import Vllm\nfrom fastapi import FastAPI\nimport uvicorn\nimport faiss\nimport numpy as np\n\n# 配置参数\nVLLM_API_KEY = \"sk-123456789abcdef\"\nVLLM_API_URL = \"http://localhost:11435/v1\"\nVLLM_MODEL_NAME = \"qwen3.5-9b\"\nEMBED_DIM = 768  # 默认嵌入维度\nPERSIST_DIR = \"/home/zigaa/.openclaw/workspace/workspace-develop/data/index\"\n\n# 简化嵌入模型（使用硬编码向量或简单逻辑）\ndef get_embedding(text):\n    \"\"\"简化嵌入：使用固定向量（实际应用中应使用真实嵌入模型）\"\"\"\n    import hashlib\n    hash_val = hashlib.md5(text.encode()).hexdigest()\n    # 确保维度为 EMBED_DIM (768)\n    hash_val = (hash_val * (768 // len(hash_val) + 1))[:768]\n    vector = [int(c, 16) / 15.0 for c in hash_val]  # 归一化到 [-1, 1]\n    return vector\n\n# 配置 LLM 模型\nprint(\"=\" * 50)\nprint(\"RAG 系统服务启动（vLLM + 自定义 FAISS + 简化嵌入）\")\nprint(\"=\" * 50)\n\nprint(\"\\n配置 LLM 模型...\")\nllm = Vllm(\n    model=VLLM_MODEL_NAME,\n    api_url=VLLM_API_URL,\n    vllm_kwargs={\n        \"model\": VLLM_MODEL_NAME,\n        \"api_key\": VLLM_API_KEY\n    }\n)\nprint(f\"  LLM 模型：{llm}\")\n\n# 配置简化嵌入模型\nprint(\"\\n配置简化嵌入模型...\")\nprint(\"  使用简化嵌入逻辑（硬编码向量）\")\n\n# 配置向量数据库（自定义 FAISS）\nprint(\"\\n配置向量数据库...\")\nfaiss_index = faiss.IndexFlatL2(EMBED_DIM)\nfaiss_dir = os.path.join(PERSIST_DIR, \"faiss_index\")\nos.makedirs(faiss_dir, exist_ok=True)\nprint(f\"  向量数据库目录：{faiss_dir}\")\n\n# 加载文档\nprint(\"\\n加载文档...\")\ndocuments = [\n    Document(text=\"RAG 是一种检索增强生成技术，它结合了检索和生成两种能力。\"),\n    Document(text=\"这是一个简单的 RAG 系统示例，使用 LlamaIndex 框架。\"),\n    Document(text=\"LlamaIndex 是一个用于构建 RAG 应用的框架。\")\n]\n\n# 分词\nprint(\"\\n分词...\")\nnode_parser = SentenceSplitter(chunk_size=500, chunk_overlap=50)\nnodes = node_parser.get_nodes_from_documents(documents)\ntexts = [node.text for node in nodes]\nprint(f\"  文本数量：{len(texts)}\")\n\n# 生成嵌入\nprint(\"\\n生成嵌入...\")\nembeddings = np.array([get_embedding(text) for text in texts], dtype=np.float32)\nprint(f\"  嵌入维度：{embeddings.shape}\")\n\n# 添加索引\nprint(\"\\n添加索引...\")\nfaiss_index.add(embeddings)\n# 保存到子目录（避免覆盖目录）\nfaiss_dir_file = faiss_dir + \"/index.faiss\"\nos.makedirs(os.path.dirname(faiss_dir_file), exist_ok=True)\nfaiss.write_index(faiss_index, faiss_dir_file)\nprint(f\"  索引保存成功：{faiss_dir_file}\")\n\n# 创建服务上下文\nprint(\"\\n创建服务上下文...\")\nservice_context = ServiceContext.from_defaults(\n    llm=llm,\n    embed_model=lambda x: get_embedding(x)\n)\n\n# 构建索引\nprint(\"\\n构建 RAG 索引...\")\nindex = VectorStoreIndex.from_documents(\n    documents=documents,\n    service_context=service_context\n)\nprint(\"  索引构建成功！\")\n\n# 测试查询\nprint(\"\\n测试查询...\")\nquery_engine = index.as_query_engine()\nresponse = query_engine.query(\"什么是 RAG?\")\nprint(f\"  回答：{response}\")\n\nprint(\"\\n\" + \"=\" * 50)\nprint(\"RAG 系统服务启动成功！\")\nprint(\"=\" * 50)\n\n# 启动 FastAPI 服务\napp = FastAPI(title=\"RAG API\")\n\n@app.get(\"/query\")\nasync def query(query_text: str):\n    response = index.as_query_engine().query(query_text)\n    return {\"answer\": str(response)}\n\n@app.get(\"/health\")\nasync def health():\n    return {\"status\": \"ok\", \"service\": \"RAG API\"}\n\nprint(\"\\n启动 FastAPI 服务...\")\nprint(\"  访问地址：http://localhost:8000\")\nprint(\"  健康检查：http://localhost:8000/health\")\nprint(\"  查询接口：http://localhost:8000/query?query_text=你的问题\")\n\nuvicorn.run(app, host=\"0.0.0.0\", port=8000, log_level=\"warning\")"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"vllm","model":"qwen3.5-9b","usage":{"input":78564,"output":1359,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79923,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776325654358,"responseId":"chatcmpl-82036a55e4b37aaf"}}
