{"type":"message","id":"8ce33680","parentId":"67eb3871","timestamp":"2026-04-16T07:51:56.480Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的，大哥。最终版服务脚本已修复（移除 `as_query_engine()` 调用）。\n\n**下一步：启动服务。**\n\n**立即执行：启动服务。**\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_76ae5fd1f4904f9d8813e7b1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/zigaa/.openclaw/workspace/workspace-develop && uv run python rag_service_final.py &"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"vllm","model":"qwen3.5-9b","usage":{"input":103673,"output":83,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103756,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776325915007,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b4330a1a3d80aef3"}}
