{"type":"message","id":"f6ed9415","parentId":"558f59e1","timestamp":"2026-04-16T09:04:26.976Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"大哥，我在！👋\n\n服务已启动，正在运行中。您提到的远程访问问题，需要检查两点：\n\n1. **服务监听地址**：已设置为 `0.0.0.0:8000`（允许外部访问）\n2. **防火墙设置**：需要确保防火墙允许 8000 端口\n\n**快速检查**：\n```bash\n# 检查 8000 端口是否监听\nnetstat -tlnp | grep 8000\n\n# 检查防火墙\nsudo ufw status\n# 或\nsudo firewall-cmd --list-all\n```\n\n**需要我帮您**：\n1. 检查防火墙状态\n2. 开放 8000 端口\n3. 重启服务确保监听外部地址\n\n请告诉我下一步，大哥！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"vllm","model":"qwen3.5-9b","usage":{"input":96664,"output":179,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96843,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776330263170,"responseId":"chatcmpl-84607c20a66fd57d"}}
